<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Text — takes 3 columns, left-aligned -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="text-primary text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-3">Since 2008</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl heading-display text-gray-800 mb-6">Smart Card Manufacturer</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Proud Tek has been manufacturing and supplying smart cards for public traffic, access control, cashless payment, etc. since 2008. We have supplied various smart cards to reputable public traffic companies from Mexico, Turkey, Lithuania, and other countries. We also make smart cards in the form factor of key fobs and wristbands and are honored to supply them to Fortune 500 companies.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          In addition to smart cards, we also offer RFID laundry tags that are perfect for tracking garments. Our quick delivery, perfect reading range, and stable performance win us more and more happy wholesalers and laundry shop customers.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/about"
          class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors font-medium"
        >
          About Proud Tek
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats — takes 2 columns, provides visual weight on the right -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">108+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Global Clients</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">50+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Countries</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">46+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Product SKUs</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">5M+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Cards/Month</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
